formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
This certificate is being issued for RERA compliance for the Company Anmol Construction Compnay  and the project Anmol 					
Ambience and is based on the records and documents produced before me and explanations provided to me by the					
management of the Company based on the verification of books of account till 31.05.2022 and subject to following notes :					
Notes 					
1	This certificate has been issued on the basis of verification of unaudited books of accounts of the project upto 31.05.2022.				
2	The estimated cost of project as per column no A of 1(ii)(a)(iii), (b) and   has been taken on the basis of estimates made				
	by manangement.				
3	Promoter has opened 2 RERA Account, one at the time of registration of project and other at the time of taking the project				
	loan in accordance with the terms of sanction of bank. The promoter has applied for the change in bank account through				
	bank account change. For which RERA Authority approved application on 15th June 2020.  promoter has deposited				
	Rs.84.00 Lacs collected from allottes in a Old RERA Account , Rs. 1670.40 Lacs in existing RERA Accountand balance				
	Rs.172.50 Lacs in other than RERA Account. 				
4	Out of total receipt excluding GST of Rs. 1926.90 lacs from members, Rs. 172.50 Lacs has been deposited In Other than RERA Account.				
5	Since the amount in RERA account as per prefiled amount is Rs. 8237 as on 22.01.2020 is showing and the same is				
	ineditable, the amount of Rs. 6460/- has been adjusted from the amount of deposit during the period in RERA Account				
6	Estimated interest is towards  funds, which promoters may take from banks, or finacial institution or money lenders in				
	case of need in the future, as estimated by the management and same is relied upon by us				
7	KYC Details and Mobile Number of Allotees has been provided by the management and the same has not been verified by us.
